title: UMBRA Prisma Photo Display
description:
UMBRA Prisma Photo Display
Design: Sung Wook Park

Add new dimension to your photo displays with this prismatic, 4x4", 5x7", or 8x10" wire frame, in which a photo floats between two panes of glass. Can alternately sit on the desk or be hung on the wall. Multi Photo Display Holds 3 5x7" photos. Comes in Black, Matte Brass, Chrome, and Copper.
